<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.2">
<l>maiya kaṇṇāṇ malarmēluṟaivā ḷuṟaimārpiṉaṉ</l>
<l>ceyya kōlat taṭaṅkaṇṇaṉ viṇṇōr perumāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>moyya collā licaimālaikaḷētti yuḷḷap peṟṟēṉ</l>
<l>veyya nōykaṇ muḻutum viyaṉñālattu vīyavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He on whose chest stays she with kajal eye, she who stays on the blossom,</l>
<l>Kṛṣṇa with red beautiful large eyes, the great lord of the celstials,</l>
<l>praising him in a musical garland with assorted words I have received [him] in [my] heart</l>
<l>so that all of the hot pains in the wide world will perish.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
